2026-05-18T06:18:36.5709922Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-18T06:18:36.5710640Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T06:18:36.5711393Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T06:18:36.5712263Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T06:18:36.5713224Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
